data.description: TURN THE KEY and walk in to this beautiful brick home! Foyer opens to large den with gas fireplace, Kitchen complete with stainless appliances, room off kitchen could be used as dining room, office or 5th bedroom.   Large mudroom /Laundry room with plenty of storage and a Culligan water softener salt system.  This 4 bedroom (could be 5  if needed), 3 bath spacious split  floor plan is the perfect family home.  The Primary Suite features tray ceiling, spa tub, double vanity, and large walk-in  his and her closets.   You will enjoy the covered patio,  oversized fenced backyard and sprinkler system for that manicured lawn.  Home equipped with ring cameras, and several spotlight cameras.  Looking for a work area, this Large covered carport with storage room  wired for power is the perfect addition.   A must see!  Call today
